#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:47
msgid ""
"Recommended format: <code>Model number + core product keywords + "
"specifications/attributes</code>"
msgstr "推荐格式: <code>型号 + 核心产品词 + 规格/属性</code>"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:52
msgid "Short Description"
msgstr "短描述"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:54
#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:69
msgid "Writing Guidelines:"
msgstr "写作指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:56
msgid ""
"The short description should naturally include high-frequency user search "
msgstr "简短描述应该自然地包含高频用户搜索"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:56
msgid "keywords"
msgstr "关键词"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:56
msgid " or "
msgstr " 或 "

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:56
msgid "long-tail keywords"
msgstr "长尾关键词"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:57
msgid "Place important keywords at the beginning to improve keyword weighting"
msgstr "将重要关键词放在开头以提高关键词权重"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:58
msgid "Recommended length is between "
msgstr "建议长度介于"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:58
msgid "100-160"
msgstr "100-160"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:58
msgid " characters, providing sufficient value without being overly lengthy"
msgstr "字符，提供足够的价值，但又不会太长"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:59
msgid ""
"Use clear and concise language, avoiding excessive technical terminology"
msgstr "使用清晰简洁的语言，避免过多的技术术语"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:60
msgid ""
"Highlight unique product advantages, such as materials, performance, price, "
"usage scenarios, etc."
msgstr "突出产品独有的优势，比如材质、性能、价格、使用场景等。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:71
msgid ""
"It is recommended to use relevant keywords in the details, no less than 5 "
"times, evenly distributed throughout the page."
msgstr "建议在详情中使用相关关键词，不少于5次，均匀分布于整个页面。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:72
msgid ""
"Replace all pronouns in the details with keywords - use specific names "
"instead of words like \"it\" whenever possible."
msgstr ""
"用关键词替换详细信息中的所有代词 - 尽可能使用具体名称而不是“它”之类的词。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid "Each paragraph in the details should not exceed "
msgstr "详细信息中的每个段落不应超过"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid "500"
msgstr "500"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid ""
" characters. If exceeded, split into paragraphs. The full text should have a "
"minimum of "
msgstr "字符。如果超过，则拆分成段落。全文至少应包含"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid "1000"
msgstr "1000"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:73
msgid " characters."
msgstr " 字符。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:74
msgid ""
"Ensure original content in the details. Do not copy directly from the "
"internet. Page similarity within the website should not exceed "
msgstr "确保内容细节原创。请勿直接从互联网复制。网站内页面相似度不得超过 "

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:74
msgid "30%"
msgstr "30%"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:74
msgid "."
msgstr "。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:83
msgid "Category Selection Guidelines:"
msgstr "类别选择指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:85
msgid ""
"Select the most relevant categories for your product to improve "
"discoverability."
msgstr "为您的产品选择最相关的类别以提高可发现性。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:86
msgid "Use specific categories rather than generic ones when possible."
msgstr "尽可能使用特定类别而不是通用类别。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:87
msgid ""
"Avoid selecting too many categories - 2-4 relevant categories are "
"recommended."
msgstr "避免选择太多类别 - 建议选择 2-4 个相关类别。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:88
msgid ""
"Check existing categories before creating new ones to maintain consistency."
msgstr "在创建新类别之前，请检查现有类别以保持一致性。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:97
msgid "Tag Usage Guidelines:"
msgstr "标签使用指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:99
msgid ""
"Use tags to highlight specific features, materials, or use cases of your "
"product."
msgstr "使用标签突出显示产品的特定功能、材料或用例。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:100
msgid "Tags should be single words or short phrases separated by commas."
msgstr "标签应该是用逗号分隔的单个单词或短语。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:101
msgid "Focus on important keywords that customers might search for."
msgstr "关注客户可能搜索的重要关键词。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:102
msgid ""
"Avoid duplicate tags and excessive tagging - 5-10 relevant tags are "
"sufficient."
msgstr "避免重复标签和过度标签 - 5-10 个相关标签就足够了。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:109
msgid "Download"
msgstr "下载"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:111
msgid "Downloadable Content Guidelines:"
msgstr "可下载内容指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:113
msgid "Upload high-quality files in supported formats (PDF, DOC, ZIP, etc.)."
msgstr "上传支持格式（PDF、DOC、ZIP 等）的高质量文件。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:114
msgid "Ensure files are virus-free and safe for users to download."
msgstr "确保文件无病毒且可供用户安全下载。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:115
msgid "Provide clear file descriptions to help users understand content."
msgstr "提供清晰的文件描述以帮助用户理解内容。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:116
msgid "Compress large files to reduce download time and server load."
msgstr "压缩大文件以减少下载时间和服务器负载。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:123
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:125
msgid "FAQ Creation Guidelines:"
msgstr "常见问题解答创建指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:127
msgid ""
"Address common customer questions about product features, usage, and "
"specifications."
msgstr "解答客户关于产品功能、用途和规格的常见问题。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:128
msgid "Write clear, concise questions and detailed, helpful answers."
msgstr "写出清晰、简洁的问题和详细、有用的答案。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:129
msgid "Organize FAQs in order of importance or frequency of questions."
msgstr "写出清晰、简洁的问题和详细、有用的答案。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:130
msgid "Regularly update FAQs based on customer feedback and new questions."
msgstr "根据客户反馈和新问题定期更新常见问题解答。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:137
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "属性"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:139
msgid "Product Attributes Guidelines:"
msgstr "产品属性指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:141
msgid "Include all relevant technical specifications and product details."
msgstr "包括所有相关的技术规格和产品详细信息。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:142
msgid "Use consistent naming conventions for attribute keys."
msgstr "对属性键使用一致的命名约定。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:143
msgid "Provide accurate measurements and specifications."
msgstr "提供准确的测量和规格。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:144
msgid "Avoid duplicate attributes and ensure all values are filled in."
msgstr "避免重复的属性并确保填写所有值。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:152
msgid "Product Model/SKU"
msgstr "产品型号/SKU"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:154
msgid "SKU Management Guidelines:"
msgstr "SKU管理指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:156
msgid "Enter a unique product model number or SKU to identify your product."
msgstr "请输入唯一的商品型号或 SKU 以识别您的商品。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:157
msgid ""
"Use alphanumeric characters, hyphens, and underscores for best compatibility."
msgstr "为了获得最佳兼容性，请使用字母数字字符、连字符和下划线。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:158
msgid "Avoid using spaces and special characters in SKUs."
msgstr "SKU中请避免使用空格和特殊字符。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:159
msgid ""
"Keep SKUs consistent in format across similar products for easier management."
msgstr "为了便于管理，请保持类似产品的 SKU 格式一致。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:160
msgid "SKUs help with inventory tracking and e-commerce integration."
msgstr "SKU有助于库存跟踪和电子商务集成。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:168
msgid "Long-tail Keywords"
msgstr "长尾关键词"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:170
msgid "Long-tail Keywords Guidelines:"
msgstr "长尾关键词指南："

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:172
msgid ""
"Enter basic keywords to generate related long-tail variations automatically."
msgstr "输入基本关键词，即可自动生成相关的长尾关键词变体。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:173
msgid ""
"Long-tail keywords typically have lower competition and higher conversion "
"rates."
msgstr "长尾关键词通常竞争较小，转化率较高。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:174
msgid ""
"Use generated keywords in product titles, descriptions, and meta fields."
msgstr "在产品标题、描述和元字段中使用生成的关键词。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:175
msgid "Focus on specific customer intents and use cases for better targeting."
msgstr "关注具体的客户意图和使用场景，以实现更精准的定位。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:176
msgid ""
"Review and customize generated keywords to match your specific product niche."
msgstr "查看并自定义生成的关键词，使其与您的特定产品领域相匹配。"

#: includes/class-jc-post-meta-box.php:184
#: includes/metabox/class-jc-product-videourl-metabox.php:25
